What does Dfreemedia provide and how can it help?

About the 10$ giveaway
We will choose five lucky winners from the first 1000 users to receive a free 10$
How to join? simply join Dfreemedia, That's all! just harry up you must be one of the first 1000 users
How we choose the winners?
1-once we hit 100 users we will pick a random winner with the help of a random number generator and see which user id matches the given number
2-then another winner once we hit 300,
3-again another winner at 500
4-Winner at 700
5-and finally a winner at 1000
So if you were early you will have a better chance of winning
How will winners receive their money?
    once we hit 1500 we will send friend invites to those winners and contact them on how they can receive their money on our app Dfreemedia, if any didn't reply or accept the friend request within 7 days we will choose another winner, Winners will receive their money by PayPal.
In case a winner can't receive money by PayPal he has two options: 1- Give us one of his accounts and we will make a purchase with 10$ for him 2- Or let us choose another winner
Good Luck all!
Hope you like it, you deserve more than that guys. Remember you must be one of the first 1000 users, so hurry up
